
'''Azuma Adams''' (Wɔ woo no December da ɛtɔ so 28, afe 1997) yɛ Ghana ni bɔɔl bɔfo a osi akan sɛ atena mu gyinafo. W’asi akan mprɛnnu ama [[Ghana]] mma a wonni mfie 17 bɔɔl bɔ kuo no. Na ɔka ekuo a ɛsii akan wɔ akansie a ɛne 2012 FIFA mmaa a wonni mfie 17 akansie, 2014 2012 FIFA mmaa a wonni mfie 17 akansie ne 2016 FIFA mmaa a wonni mfie 20 akansie.
